{"article_id":"etfw7LwrLxxuIqEr","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"President Donald Trump announced a deal","depth":5},{"id":1,"text":"to end the partial government shutdown from the Rose Garden Friday afternoon .","depth":5},{"id":2,"text":"Federal workers will receive back pay immediately .","depth":4},{"id":3,"text":"\" I am very proud to announce","depth":8},{"id":4,"text":"we have reached a deal","depth":9},{"id":5,"text":"to end the shutdown","depth":10},{"id":6,"text":"and reopen the federal government , ''","depth":10},{"id":7,"text":"Trump said .","depth":7},{"id":8,"text":"`` In a short while I will sign a bill","depth":8},{"id":9,"text":"to open the government for three weeks . ''","depth":8},{"id":10,"text":"`` I want to thank all of the incredible workers and their amazing families","depth":9},{"id":11,"text":"who have showed extraordinary devotion in the wake of the hardship , ''","depth":9},{"id":12,"text":"Trump said .","depth":8},{"id":13,"text":"President Trump will sign a continuing resolution","depth":6},{"id":14,"text":"that will fund the government until February 15 .","depth":6},{"id":15,"text":"In the meantime , the White House will continue negotiations with lawmakers over border security .","depth":5},{"id":16,"text":"He assured","depth":7},{"id":17,"text":"that Democrats have promised border security ,","depth":8},{"id":18,"text":"with barriers being part of a negotiated package .","depth":8},{"id":19,"text":"Opening the government today does not include any down payment or funding for the wall .","depth":8},{"id":20,"text":"- Bill is similar to those","depth":9},{"id":21,"text":"he rejected in December and this week -","depth":9},{"id":22,"text":"If talks fail :","depth":10},{"id":23,"text":"another shutdown or a national emergency ,","depth":10},{"id":24,"text":"Trump says","depth":9},{"id":25,"text":"- BNO News","depth":10},{"id":26,"text":"( @ BNONews )","depth":10},{"id":27,"text":"January 25 , 2019","depth":9},{"id":28,"text":"Democrats have been saying for weeks","depth":6},{"id":29,"text":"they ' ll negotiate on wall funding","depth":7},{"id":30,"text":"when the government is open .","depth":7},{"id":31,"text":"POTUS is now giving them yet ANOTHER opportunity","depth":7},{"id":32,"text":"to come to the table .","depth":7},{"id":33,"text":"Americans will be able to judge for themselves","depth":7},{"id":34,"text":"whether Democrats are truly serious about securing our border .","depth":7},{"id":35,"text":"- Mark Meadows","depth":6},{"id":36,"text":"( @ RepMarkMeadows )","depth":6},{"id":37,"text":"January 25 , 2019","depth":5},{"id":38,"text":"`` Walls should not be controversial , ''","depth":5},{"id":39,"text":"Trump .","depth":5},{"id":40,"text":"`` No border security works","depth":5},{"id":41,"text":"without barriers . ''","depth":5},{"id":42,"text":"President Trump Delivers Remarks","depth":5},{"id":43,"text":"Regarding the Shutdown","depth":5},{"id":44,"text":"https : //t.co/ouqsHy5Fie","depth":5},{"id":45,"text":"- The White House","depth":7},{"id":46,"text":"( @ WhiteHouse )","depth":7},{"id":47,"text":"January 25 , 2019","depth":6},{"id":48,"text":"`` If we make a fair deal","depth":6},{"id":49,"text":"the American people will be proud of their government , ''","depth":6},{"id":50,"text":"Trump said .","depth":5},{"id":51,"text":"`` If we do n't get a fair deal from Congress","depth":7},{"id":52,"text":"the government will shut down again","depth":7},{"id":53,"text":"or I will use the powers","depth":8},{"id":54,"text":"afforded to me under the laws","depth":9},{"id":55,"text":"and afforded to me under the Constitution of the United States","depth":9},{"id":56,"text":"to address this emergency . ''","depth":7},{"id":57,"text":"According to the President ,","depth":6},{"id":58,"text":"a fair deal would include funding for a wall .","depth":6},{"id":59,"text":"President Trump was joined in the Rose Garden by Vice President Mike Pence and a number of his Cabinet officials .","depth":2}],"relation